query:
SELECT c.name, c.relationship, c.flags, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT cp.phoneNumber) as phones, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ce.email) as emails
FROM contacts c
LEFT JOIN contactPhones cp ON c.id = cp.contactId
LEFT JOIN contactEmails ce ON c.id = ce.contactId
WHERE c.propertyId = (SELECT id FROM properties WHERE addressLine1 LIKE '%285 Sw 12th%' AND city = 'Pompano Beach')
GROUP BY c.id, c.name, c.relationship, c.flags;
